# Auth & onboarding

Read **docs/contracts/flow-auth-onboarding.md** before changing sign-in, session restore, or onboarding flags.

For end-to-end invite behavior also read **docs/contracts/flow-invite-to-rally.md** (Loop A).

## Required patterns

1. Pending deep links stored on signed-out invite; replay once after auth.
2. OAuth / magic link callbacks must not block the main thread at module load.
3. Coach mark flags persist — do not reset on every app launch.

Contract status: **draft**.
